Privacy Policy for Willow: Self Discovery

Last Updated: 25 Nov. 2024

1. Information We Collect

We collect the following information to provide and improve our services:
	1.	Personal Information:
	•	Name, email, and other details provided during account creation.
	2.	Demographic Information:
	•	Age, gender, or other demographic details.
	3.	Usage Data:
	•	Interaction data such as completed personality tests and journaling entries.
	4.	Device Data:
	•	Information about your device, such as operating system and app version.

2. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected data to:
	•	Provide personalized insights and recommendations.
	•	Improve app functionality and user experience.
	•	Conduct marketing activities.

3. Data Sharing

	•	We Do Not Share Your Data: Your information is not shared with third parties for any reason, except as necessary to operate the app (e.g., third-party tools).
	•	Third-Party Tools: We use services like Firebase and Supabase for app analytics and backend operations. These tools may process your data securely on our behalf.

4. Your Rights

You have the right to:
	1.	Access or Delete Your Data:
	•	To request data deletion or access, contact us at:
Email: mullermtg@gmail.com
	2.	Limit Data Collection:
	•	Some features may require data collection. Choosing not to provide certain information may limit app functionality.

5. Data Security

We take data security seriously and implement the following measures:
	•	Use of secure servers via row-level security provided by Supabase.
	•	Encryption of sensitive information.

While we strive to protect your data, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure. By using the app, you acknowledge and accept this risk.

6. Sensitive Data

The app collects sensitive information such as personality test results. This data is used solely to provide personalized insights and is stored securely.

7. Children’s Privacy

We do not knowingly collect data from children under the age of 13 without parental consent. If you believe your child has provided personal information, please contact us at mullermtg@gmail.com to request its removal.

8. International Users

The app is available globally, primarily in Western countries. By using the app, you consent to the processing of your information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.

9. Contact Us

For questions, concerns, or data-related inquiries, contact us at:
Email: mullermtg@gmail.com
